        "created_at": "2018-10-04T03:28:20.000Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/wine.asp?iWine=173832\"><strong>1959 Ch\u00e2teau Chasse-Spleen</strong></a> <em>- France, Bordeaux, M\u00e9doc, Moulis en M\u00e9doc (9/29/2018)</em><br>\nIn wonderful condition, drinking beautifully. Complex aromatics of briary fruits, earth, lead pencil, autumnal leaves and bitter chocolate. It has good presence in the mouth, caressing the gums with savoury flavours. There\u2019s a core of cassis and a finish that has a lick of saline minerality. Such great poise and balance.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
